e creative entrepreneurs imagined new ways to use them. The making of Moore=
&#8217;s Law is as much a story of manufacturing experts, supply chain spec=
ialists, and marketing managers as it is about physicists or electrical eng=
ineers.</em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size:=
 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>That&#8217;s just one =
