d $1,000 genome programs, through which they awarded $230 million to 97 res=
earch labs and industrial scientists.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rg=
b(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Pri=
vate enterprise played a role, too. Illumina, which now employs nearly 10,0=
