</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Moore&#8217;s Law has clearly played its part &=
#8211; providing the computational foundation for managing and analyzing th=
e large datasets involved in genomics &#8211; but the Genome Law has primar=
ily been fueled by domain-specific advancements in biotech and chemistry fr=
