style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Let&#8217;s wrap this up on a practical note. </span><=
strong>Exponential technology curves aren&#8217;t just beautiful, they&#821=
7;re investible.&#160;</strong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">A key pillar of Not Bo=
ring Capital&#8217;s Fund III thesis is that enough of these curves are hit=
ting the right spot that previously impossible or uneconomical ideas now pe=
ncil out.&#160;</p><div class=3D"captioned-image-container-static" style=3D=
